nodes.text: Kuna's Fist was a location in the Moddell sector of the Outer Rim Territories. In preparation for the Battle of Endor in 4 ABY, Corporal Ractivelle of the Stardust unit compiled a report on the navigation of the Moddell sector on behalf of the Rebel Alliance, and featured Kuna's Fist.

Before the Battle of Endor, the map of the Moddell sector and the accompanying reports were archived in The Rebel Files, a data archive safeguarding secret rebel documents and information. In 34 ABY, The Rebel Files were rediscovered and ultimately given to the Resistance.
Kuna's Fist was first mentioned in Star Wars: Build the Millennium Falcon 18, a canon magazine first released in 2015 and published by De Agostini.
